com.serena.dmclient.api
Class ProjectDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.ProjectDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionsLcObjectDetails, DimensionsObjectDetails
public class ProjectDetails
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains details of a new project that is to be created. It does not perform any validation, but is merely a data object for information to pass to the create project operation.

getKeepStage

public boolean getKeepStage()
Returns the "KeepStage" flag for the project to be created. true keep the stage of the item revisions from the source project, false reset the stage of all items in the new project to the initial stage.

Returns:
flag

public void setKeepStageFlag(boolean isKeepStage)
Sets the "IsKeepStage" flag for the project to be created. If this flag is not set, false is the default. true keep the stage of the item revisions from the source project, false reset the stage of all items in the new project to the initial stage.

Parameters:
isKeepStage - flag.

getCMRulesFlag

public char getCMRulesFlag()
Returns the "CMRules" flag for the project to be created. The flag could be: ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_DEFAULT == 'X' ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_ON == 'Y' ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_OFF == 'N'

Returns:
flagCMRules

setCMRulesFlag

public void setCMRulesFlag(char cmRules)
Sets the "CMRules" flag for the project to be created. The flag could be: ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_DEFAULT == 'X' ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_ON == 'Y' ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_OFF == 'N' If this flag is not set, ProjectDetails.PROJECT_CM_RULES_DEFAULT is the default.

Parameters:
cmRules - the value for the "CMRules" flag as above.
